The Mastercard Foundation, United States International University-Africa (USIU-Africa), and Arizona State University (ASU) announced the launch of the Mastercard Foundation Scholars Program e-Learning Initiative, which, building on what was learned during the COVID-19 disruption, will over the next five years enable more than 600,000 university students to successfully pursue their studies online, from anywhere across Africa. Read on. Find out more about Mastercard Foundation in Africa.